OL,3,C'Heartbreaking' memories of Miners'
OL,4,CStrike pulled together for 40th
OL,5,Canniversary
OL,7,FThe anniversary is being marked by a
OL,8,Fnew exhibition at the National Coal
OL,9,FMining Museum, in Wakefield, and CEO
OL,10,FLynn Dunning said the aim has been to
OL,11,Fmake sure the perspectives of all
OL,12,Fthose involved are represented.
OL,14,FShe said this includes the memories of
OL,15,Fthe miners and their families who were
OL,16,Fon strike for a year.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/12
