OL,3,C'Heartbreaking' memories of Miners'
OL,4,CStrike pulled together for 40th
OL,5,Canniversary
OL,7,FBut it also includes those who decided
OL,8,Fthey had to return to work and those
OL,9,Fin the coalfields where most miners
OL,10,Fdefied the call to walk out from
OL,11,FNational Union of Mineworkers
OL,12,Fpresident Arthur Scargill ` most
OL,13,Fnotably in Nottinghamshire.
OL,15,FMs Dunning told the PA news agency:
OL,16,F"The exhibition is really to try and
OL,17,Fgive a voice to as many different
OL,18,Fopinions and experiences as possible.
OL,20,F"Quite often we hear a lot from the
OL,21,Fmen who were on strike.
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@AOU
