OL,3,C'Heartbreaking' memories of Miners'
OL,4,CStrike pulled together for 40th
OL,5,Canniversary
OL,7,FMs Dunning said: "It's quite shocking,
OL,8,Feven today, after 40 years, to hear
OL,9,Fabout somebody eating their pet rabbit
OL,10,Fbecause they had nothing else to put
OL,11,Fon the table.
OL,13,F"Those are stories that we all need to
OL,14,Fhear and experience."
OL,16,FShe said: "This exhibition takes the
OL,17,Fpolitics out of it and it's really
OL,18,Fabout what those people experienced
OL,19,Fand just how difficult it was.
OL,26,@oD@ROUuD@AOUvD@UO]xD@KOU
