OL,3,C'Heartbreaking' memories of Miners'
OL,4,CStrike pulled together for 40th
OL,5,Canniversary
OL,7,F"And, the long-term impact that that
OL,8,Fexperience has had on those families
OL,9,Fand those communities comes across
OL,10,Freally strongly as well."
OL,12,FShe said: "It's still such a raw
OL,13,Ftopic. It's still such an emotional
OL,14,Ftopic for many people, what happened
OL,15,Fto those communities socially,
OL,16,Feconomically, culturally.
OL,18,F"You can still see the impact of that
OL,19,Fin those communities today."
