OL,3,C'Heartbreaking' memories of Miners'
OL,4,CStrike pulled together for 40th
OL,5,Canniversary
OL,7,FExhibition curator Anne Bradley said
OL,8,Fthe show does feature some artefacts
OL,9,Fbut its core are the first-hand
OL,10,Faccounts from those who were there,
OL,11,Fwhich she has collected through a
OL,12,Fseries of interviews.
OL,14,FMs Bradley said that her interviews
OL,15,Fshowed that many of the old enmities
OL,16,Fare still there. Some contributors
OL,17,Fwould only take part on condition of
OL,18,Fanonymity.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/12
