OL,3,C'Heartbreaking' memories of Miners'
OL,4,CStrike pulled together for 40th
OL,5,Canniversary
OL,7,FAnd she is aware that some visitors
OL,8,Fwill refuse to go into the parts of
OL,9,Fthe exhibitions focusing on the
OL,10,Fexperiences of who they would see as
OL,11,F"scabs".
OL,13,FMs Bradley said: "We're a national
OL,14,Fmuseum and we have to reflect what was
OL,15,Fhappening in all the different
OL,16,Fcoalfields in England.
OL,18,F"I think it's quite a well known
OL,19,Fstory, the story of striking miners on
OL,20,Fthe picket lines, and the policing.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@GO]uD@ROUzD@AOU
