OL,3,C'Heartbreaking' memories of Miners'
OL,4,CStrike pulled together for 40th
OL,5,Canniversary
OL,7,F"I think those stories of those who
OL,8,Feither chose not to strike or who
OL,9,Fcouldn't because of the position that
OL,10,Fthey were in or the unions that they
OL,11,Fwere working for, and those that made
OL,12,Fthat decision to go back early, are
OL,13,Fstories that we don't hear.
OL,15,F"And this is a really good opportunity
OL,16,Ffor us to diversify our collections,
OL,17,Fcollect those stories and those voices
OL,18,Fwhile we still have the chance."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@`O]
