OL,4,CStrike pulled together for 40th
OL,5,Canniversary
OL,7,FShe said: "We'd like to provide the
OL,8,Fopportunity for our visitors to
OL,9,Fperhaps have little bit of empathy, to
OL,10,Flook 40 years on and see that people
OL,11,Fwere making decisions that they had no
OL,12,Fidea that 40 years on could still lead
OL,13,Fto them not speaking to members of
OL,14,Ftheir families, not speaking to
OL,15,Ffriends.
OL,17,F"We're not asking anybody to change
OL,18,Ftheir opinion of the strike but we're
OL,19,Fhoping that people might just stop and
OL,20,Fthink, maybe look at a different point
OL,21,Fof view.
